# This folder contains default images for the CMS

# Required images:
# - default-og-image.jpg (1200x630) - Default Open Graph image
# - default-avatar.png (200x200) - Default user avatar
# - default-featured.jpg (800x600) - Default featured image for posts
# - placeholder.jpg (800x600) - Placeholder image

# You can create these images using any image editor or online tools
